reviewText: Ron White is one of the best comedians around and this DVD is no exception!  Well done with great comedians.
Title: Ron White's Comedy Salute to the Troops

reviewText: I got this for my dad for Father's Day, he likes Ron and the Blue Collar guys, and especially since this was for the troops, but their were too many f-bombs,etc. for him and my step-mom. Sent his back, kept my copy. Do be advised - if you want the clean version, record it off CMT.
Title: Ron White's Comedy Salute to the Troops

reviewText: The only thing wrong with this DVD is that there isn't enough Ron White.  The other comics were OK--but there is nothing like "too much" Ron White.
summary: Ron White's Salute to the Troops

Title: Ron White's Comedy Salute to the Troops

reviewText: If you are interested in just Ron White than get Ron White: A little Unprofessional, he tells all the same jokes as on this show plus a few one liners, and a story joke about what happento him on a yacht. If you want a mix of comedians such as Alex Ramundo, Kathlien Madegan, Lewis Black along with a number of others hosted by Ron White, than by all means get this DVD
summary: It depends on what you want
